Description: Fragment from the shoulder of Fikellura painted pottery neck-amphora. Lotus flowers and buds, unjoined; below, open cable.
Curator's comments: Possibly belongs to the Altenburg Group (J 10d)
Bibliographic references: CVA British Museum 8 / Corpus Vasorum Antiquorum: Great Britain 13, British Museum 8 (Pl. GB 576, 16)
Weber 2012 / Untersuchungen zur archaischen griechischen Keramik aus anderen ägyptischen Fundorten (TD 202)
